Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:43.78,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要慢吞吞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的弹珠怎么不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.54,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皮包里那五块钱是不是你拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:20.96,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不知道 不是你还有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:31.86,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是你拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:32.98,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.74,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.86,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}敢上去！给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.10,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你脚那么脏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:01.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我埋在这里被人家偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真会乱讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还说藏在这里 你拿到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我埋在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后砖头压在上面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:43.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还在骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的啦！我没有骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你长大了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这边 这边啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆您去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:06.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找阿孝牯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}认不得路啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:17.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:18.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太太车钱还没有给呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}钱还没付哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回家去拿啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:09.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要一边吃饭一边背乘法表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然就吃饭前背一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后吃饭后再背一遍
