Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前世没修 儿子当媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孩子懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝啊！阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来洗澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进去洗澡啦 我来洗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝啊！不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.54,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你长大就有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三斤二两
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的比你多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}枝仔冰
