Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝牯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:08.98,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟阿婆回大陆去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:15.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:27.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿哈！阿哈！大卵巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了好了 换我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.06,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.42,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:04.90,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝快救它出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.18,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一流的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦 不要叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会玩就不要来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.26,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要让他玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看什么啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要跟他玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看什么啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要理他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再来再来 换我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本台消息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我英勇空军健儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:14.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天在马祖海峡上空的空战中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已击落匪米格十七飞机五架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反击伤其两架的辉煌战果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做为双十国庆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给全国同胞的最佳献礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我空军健儿以无比的沉着应战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:32.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}充分发挥了以寡敌众的革命精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赢得了全国同胞一致的喝釆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是我空军飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张乃军上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:42.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作战时 为解救友机除危
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:47.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而奋不顾身驾其座机与匪机互撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:50.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其壮烈成仁的忠贞表现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又再一次发扬光大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先烈勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}牺牲奋斗的革命精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为我空军战史上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}写下了最光辉的一页
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:05.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本台消息 蒋总统于今日上午十时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在总统府主持中华民国四十七年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}国庆纪念典礼上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}宣布空战胜利消息时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:15.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}建元在金门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么好久没来信？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我上个月还写信给他耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概是金门管制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前我每次写信给他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.88,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最多一个礼拜就会收到回信的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:35.94,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秋明的儿子 建元啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}建元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他爸爸死得很可怜喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候我在广州读中山大学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就住他那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:03.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候 他当营长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:07.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他突然得了恶性疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.70,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我坐黄包车 替他去拿药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:24.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拖车的人 突然跌了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连车灯都跌碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.70,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我当时心里 很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:39.30,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚好跌在棺材店的门口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:48.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秋明死的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秋明嫂在坐月子 生了建元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:56.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她在屋内闻到很腥的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就问她妈妈是不是卖鱼的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去看啊！根本就没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:05.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:09.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张家送来坐月子的母鸡夜啼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:13.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆说要捉去三叉路口斩首
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:14.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才会转运
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.96,0:24:35.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们要反攻大陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:36.58,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}骗人 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:38.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都没有听到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.84,0:24:40.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师说的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.28,0:24:41.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要打你一枪 我跟你讲
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.24,0:27:09.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走开 走开 看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:54.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那里有水 去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.28,0:29:44.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一家人这么多张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.28,0:29:46.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一天要多少东西来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.96,0:29:50.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你爸爸一个月薪水才六百二十块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.88,0:29:55.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己留二十块钱理发、零用
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.04,0:29:57.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}六百块家用
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:02.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又要买菜 又要给你们看病
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:05.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你爸爸身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.60,0:30:08.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你以后教书教没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.64,0:30:10.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不是要嫁人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.32,0:30:14.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们家里小孩多
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.00,0:30:17.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做大的就要牺牲点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.96,0:30:21.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你读师范不需用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.28,0:30:24.74,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以后还有书好教
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.40,0:30:31.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}女孩子读那么多书做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.12,0:30:36.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}灶头镬尾 针头线尾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.32,0:30:39.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田头地尾 三尾会了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.72,0:30:42.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.60,0:30:46.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又不是讲我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.36,0:30:47.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是讲阿忠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.36,0:30:52.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家里有一个人读师范就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.96,0:30:56.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿忠不给他读大学很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.36,0:31:04.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿忠啊 你以后还想读书
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:07.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己再去读
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.36,0:31:11.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你爸爸中学毕业就去教书
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.72,0:31:14.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到后来 还不是读了大学
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.72,0:31:16.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.08,0:31:20.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他还去南洋勤伯那里学做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.96,0:31:23.42,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有空的时候就看书
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.12,0:31:26.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别人有空就去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.16,0:31:29.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}勤伯看你爸爸不是做生意的料
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:32.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫他回广州考大学
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.36,0:31:35.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考到了中山大学
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.20,0:35:08.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁写来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.96,0:35:11.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安姑
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.60,0:35:14.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从南洋寄来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:18.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}写些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.72,0:35:24.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿庆牯读到小学三年级就没读了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.24,0:35:27.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}共产党把他扫地出门
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.92,0:35:29.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说他出身不好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.60,0:35:37.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大陆现在实行什么三面红旗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.80,0:35:39.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们炼下的铁
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.52,0:35:41.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刀子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.64,0:35:47.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}锅子、门把子、铁钉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.88,0:35:50.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连火钳什么的 统统都拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.36,0:35:52.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿去炼钢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.16,0:35:55.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}炼了一堆废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.16,0:36:04.94,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候 如果有带他出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.08,0:37:35.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝有没有考上
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.92,0:37:38.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不知道 他去学校看成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.00,0:38:23.06,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起！对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.16,0:38:30.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了啦 不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.52,0:38:31.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.84,0:38:33.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明年再考嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.00,0:38:38.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.44,0:38:39.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没考上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.92,0:38:41.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没考上就在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.16,0:38:44.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么知道没考上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.64,0:38:46.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师刚才有来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.44,0:38:47.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.96,0:38:49.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陈燕没考上在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.80,0:38:51.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你桌上也没打勾
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.04,0:38:58.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你桌上也没打勾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.44,0:39:17.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈 我考到了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.28,0:39:18.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.20,0:39:19.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我考到省立凤中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.12,0:39:22.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我桌上有一个粉笔打的勾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.20,0:39:25.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师说 桌上有勾的就是考到了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.16,0:39:28.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.80,0:39:31.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去跟你爸爸讲
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.40,0:39:36.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸 我考到了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.64,0:39:41.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我考到了省立凤中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.04,0:39:43.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的桌上有一个勾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.44,0:39:46.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师说 桌上有勾的就是考到了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.72,0:39:50.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么有个勾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.44,0:39:52.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师说 有考到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.80,0:39:55.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在桌上用粉笔划个勾
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.20,0:40:04.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 那你以后要好好的读喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.92,0:40:05.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.96,0:40:09.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿竹 阿孝怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.80,0:40:11.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他考到省立凤中
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.72,0:40:18.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝啊 阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.28,0:40:27.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你考到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.72,0:40:28.70,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.60,0:40:34.58,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.36,0:40:39.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.80,0:40:45.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿忠啊 你什么时候放榜
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.24,0:40:48.38,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.60,0:40:52.90,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝就是靠聪明跟运气
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.04,0:40:54.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他从小运气就好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.80,0:40:59.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们住新竹那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.36,0:41:01.74,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是到台北考一女中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.88,0:41:03.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个人坐火车
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.52,0:41:07.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝啊死都要跟我去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:10.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候火车上不是卖那种
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.28,0:41:12.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种用纸包的红豆冰棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:13.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.92,0:41:15.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝就一直吵说他要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.88,0:41:18.18,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}害我花了五毛钱买一根给他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.32,0:41:20.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果他一口都不给我耶
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.20,0:41:23.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不好意思跟他要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.12,0:41:25.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈那个时候不是说到火车站之后
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.72,0:41:28.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去找在那边当宪兵的阿成哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.64,0:41:30.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后阿成哥看到我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.44,0:41:32.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还说我好会喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.72,0:41:35.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然敢一个人跑那么远来考学校
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.76,0:41:36.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后就用脚踏车载我到
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.00,0:41:39.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重庆南路那边去找爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.68,0:41:40.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.60,0:41:42.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸带我到学校去考试
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.60,0:41:43.58,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在学校门口
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.72,0:41:45.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还碰到我们在新竹那个老师
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.88,0:41:47.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是你们说他很好的那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.72,0:41:50.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来我回来新竹等放榜
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.72,0:41:52.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸从台北回来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.20,0:41:55.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸回来那天 我到巷口去接他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.40,0:41:57.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸看到我就一直笑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.32,0:41:59.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后什么都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.24,0:42:00.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就问爸爸说
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.20,0:42:02.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.52,0:42:04.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸就说
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.28,0:42:07.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对！你考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.28,0:42:09.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后就开始很得意啊 在那里算说
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.60,0:42:12.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁家！谁家！谁…谁都没考上
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.80,0:42:14.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来爸告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.44,0:42:16.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是四十一名考上的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.68,0:42:18.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算术还考一百
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.28,0:42:22.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可惜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.32,0:42:27.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都不能念一女中
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.36,0:42:32.66,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是那时候念一女中就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.56,0:42:58.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.60,0:43:00.90,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆带你回大陆好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.20,0:43:04.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.52,0:43:06.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沿着大路走
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.36,0:43:09.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没过多久 过了河坝
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.32,0:43:11.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就到了梅江桥
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.40,0:43:13.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再走几步路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.24,0:43:15.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就到了弯下了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.24,0:43:18.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回大陆干什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.32,0:43:21.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.16,0:43:24.70,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆带你回祠堂拜祖先啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.72,0:44:53.78,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.40,0:44:56.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}梅江桥在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.84,0:45:00.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}梅江桥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.96,0:45:03.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他在说什么？他要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.28,0:45:05.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道在说什么 都听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.52,0:45:05.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.96,0:45:07.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.56,0:45:12.86,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}梅县的梅江桥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.24,0:45:14.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}梅江桥
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.68,0:45:16.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他在说什么桥？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.72,0:45:18.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么桥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.40,0:45:24.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.20,0:45:29.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听的懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.12,0:45:31.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.20,0:45:32.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你都听不懂了 我怎么听的懂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.60,0:46:03.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆 那里有芭乐
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.76,0:46:04.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去采
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.00,0:47:27.98,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.84,0:47:35.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要丢得太高
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.24,0:47:51.30,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.68,0:48:51.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惠兰啊 是不是停电？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.24,0:48:52.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.00,0:48:54.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来拿腊烛去点
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.00,0:49:43.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.96,0:49:49.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.96,0:49:53.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.56,0:49:55.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈 你快点来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.64,0:49:56.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.40,0:50:09.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.56,0:50:14.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.28,0:50:19.58,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.56,0:50:28.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.52,0:50:39.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.60,0:50:47.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.56,0:50:48.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.24,0:50:59.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈 医生来了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.76,0:51:02.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}医生
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.56,0:51:45.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.16,0:51:53.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.36,0:52:00.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.24,0:52:06.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.08,0:53:38.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿忠 带弟弟们过来跟爸爸握手
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.08,0:54:58.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前有人过世
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.60,0:55:01.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他家人在守灵的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.24,0:55:03.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一只猫跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.84,0:55:07.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在死者的身上跳过去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.92,0:55:10.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结果那个死者就坐了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.28,0:55:13.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以守灵的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.36,0:55:16.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}千万不要让猫跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.56,0:55:27.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我部队里的人也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.84,0:55:30.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前他们在抗日的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.40,0:55:34.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.24,0:55:36.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们在抗日的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.88,0:55:38.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}死人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.96,0:55:42.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一次部队里有人死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.52,0:55:45.98,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像尸体也被猫跳过去
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.12,0:55:46.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}死人就坐起来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.12,0:55:47.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没人顾着是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.08,0:55:51.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 还会追人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.16,0:55:51.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还会追人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.96,0:55:53.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到人就要抱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.56,0:55:56.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来有人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.80,0:56:00.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就要拿东西给他抱
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.44,0:56:06.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有抱到东西就会躺回去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.84,0:56:11.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是什么原因 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.88,0:56:13.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有人说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.36,0:56:16.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}猫身上有电还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.60,0:56:18.58,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有灵气
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.72,0:56:19.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.76,0:56:23.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.80,0:56:27.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很多人死掉都有奇奇怪怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.56,0:56:49.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿竹去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.24,0:56:52.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我洗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.76,0:56:58.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那阿孝去洗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.96,0:57:50.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.60,0:57:56.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.16,0:57:57.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.08,0:57:59.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.60,0:58:05.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.60,0:58:09.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.04,0:58:15.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分明…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.52,0:59:06.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去跟他讨点零用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.00,0:59:10.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.32,1:00:07.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.40,1:00:09.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干你娘 跟我装傻
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.00,1:00:12.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说是小生意 没赚什么钱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.96,1:00:15.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干你娘 生意那么好 还说没赚
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.92,1:00:16.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那现在要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.08,1:00:17.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把他挡下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.08,1:00:19.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊！把他挡下来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.52,1:00:20.58,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.00,1:00:23.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等他要走的时候 把他挡起来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.08,1:00:24.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不对
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.96,1:00:25.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.04,1:00:29.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然这样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.00,1:00:31.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿水你跟阿猴过去那边
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.60,1:00:32.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那边！好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.84,1:00:34.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乐咕你去路头
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.68,1:00:35.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.92,1:00:59.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种布还有吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.36,1:01:00.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不卖了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.40,1:01:02.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不卖了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.32,1:01:04.78,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那块我看看好不好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.92,1:01:05.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要收摊了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.24,1:01:08.30,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那块我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.44,1:01:09.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不卖了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.88,1:01:51.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干你娘 阿水 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.04,1:01:53.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一台摩托车都挡不住
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.12,1:01:59.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胖有什么用
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.76,1:02:05.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走啊！站在那里干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.88,1:02:09.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走啦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.40,1:02:18.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.96,1:02:21.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.52,1:02:23.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当时他从屋顶掉下来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.08,1:02:26.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把脚跌成一长一短
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.04,1:02:28.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.80,1:02:31.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差一点送他去跌打损伤店
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.12,1:02:34.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还好没送去 遇到你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.00,1:02:37.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不然小孩就受罪
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.88,1:02:40.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他哥哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.32,1:02:48.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.60,1:02:50.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.80,1:02:53.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是刘先生
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.44,1:02:54.66,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.20,1:03:21.76,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蕙兰 刘先生要走了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.56,1:03:26.70,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再见
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.20,1:03:48.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢走
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.36,1:03:49.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再见
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.04,1:03:59.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没洗就要吃
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.76,1:04:04.90,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人家的好意
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.04,1:04:06.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不喜欢也不用这样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.60,1:04:11.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正我跟芳美已经写信约好了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.88,1:04:13.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁都不要理他的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.68,1:04:17.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}圣经上说
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.32,1:04:19.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没结婚的男子
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.44,1:04:21.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有资格追求女生
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.52,1:04:50.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈 有人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.60,1:04:57.66,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘先生
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.24,1:04:59.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆 你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.32,1:05:01.88,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在大树下 遇到老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.00,1:05:03.06,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她迷了路
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.20,1:05:04.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就把她带回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.36,1:05:07.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三轮车钱我也付过了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.92,1:05:10.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.92,1:05:13.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}芭乐
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.20,1:05:37.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作弊啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.92,1:05:38.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 五班的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.08,1:05:41.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 他把小抄贴在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.00,1:05:44.38,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 你看看 贴这么整齐
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.56,1:05:45.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这要花好多功夫
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.64,1:05:47.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要花多少时间啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.96,1:05:49.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你把这些时间多念点书
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.88,1:05:52.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多看点历史地理不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.20,1:05:53.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你头脑不错
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.00,1:05:55.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么做这种勾当
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.92,1:05:57.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自以为聪明
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.44,1:06:36.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放开 拿出来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.00,1:06:38.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.96,1:07:08.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很跩嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.04,1:07:12.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为什么要打他
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.80,1:07:15.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说你是赤山的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.36,1:07:16.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赤山又怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.16,1:07:17.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.68,1:07:20.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.00,1:07:22.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还敢还手
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.92,1:07:25.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次就是他吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.72,1:07:26.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.76,1:07:32.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很大尾啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.84,1:07:34.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}任你打啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.20,1:07:36.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有一个住哪？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.16,1:07:53.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.72,1:07:56.10,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个谁 王金水
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.68,1:07:58.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干什么你们
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.72,1:08:00.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师好
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.64,1:09:42.70,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.40,1:09:43.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来玩喔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.12,1:09:45.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.60,1:09:47.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在做银元
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.76,1:09:49.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做银元
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.76,1:09:52.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做银元做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.68,1:09:54.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去阎罗王那边用
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.32,1:09:57.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去阎罗王那边用啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.80,1:10:01.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆 来拍照
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.44,1:10:04.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么老了拍什么照
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.52,1:10:05.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系啦 来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.96,1:10:07.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做纪念啦 来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.72,1:10:08.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来啦 先放着
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.04,1:10:10.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来拍照啦 好不好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.52,1:10:11.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.16,1:10:23.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝 来拍照
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.88,1:10:29.94,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.88,1:11:02.02,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆来了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.72,1:11:15.18,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝 来拍照
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.96,1:11:23.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆要看那边
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.68,1:11:30.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你去搬一张椅子来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.04,1:11:56.02,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再一张
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.44,1:12:13.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在陈故副总统灵柩的左后方
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.56,1:12:14.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凝视了很久
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.28,1:12:19.34,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蒋总统伉俪
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.52,1:12:22.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在慰问了匍伏在灵柩右边的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.56,1:12:25.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陈故父总统两位公子之后
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.68,1:12:30.54,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在又转往灵帷右侧的休息室内
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.68,1:12:33.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慰问悲痛万分的陈夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.16,1:12:34.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谭详女士
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.60,1:12:39.74,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.88,1:12:41.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撞这么大力要吃鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.24,1:12:49.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.44,1:12:50.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你眼珠脱窗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.76,1:12:52.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打黑的 你看
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.68,1:12:54.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦好啦 再给你一个机会
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.44,1:12:59.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}收起来
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.96,1:13:01.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放回去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.92,1:13:04.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小流氓 你知道今天是什么日子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.16,1:13:05.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放回去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.24,1:13:06.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.16,1:13:07.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.24,1:13:08.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放回去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.56,1:13:11.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.56,1:13:13.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我出去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.04,1:13:17.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出去 快
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.00,1:13:23.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}站在这边 站好
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.20,1:13:24.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你给我站好
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.76,1:13:27.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听听这个
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.52,1:13:32.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经决定分别在台北和台中
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.64,1:13:34.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兴建土地改革纪念馆
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.36,1:13:36.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是陈副总统大殓的日子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.24,1:13:36.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.92,1:13:40.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将建在中正路及敦化路口
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.12,1:13:42.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}台中的纪念馆
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.56,1:13:45.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将建在民权路和中华路口
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.24,1:13:48.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纪念馆里面将陈列
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.00,1:13:53.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陈故副总统土地改革的有关资料
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.44,1:13:55.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干什么 小流氓
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.52,1:13:58.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小流氓
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.68,1:14:01.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还跑 给我回来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.36,1:14:02.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小流氓 可恶
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.16,1:14:05.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你给我回来 小流氓
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.44,1:14:06.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你给我回来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.92,1:14:08.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干 靠北喔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.84,1:14:14.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干你娘
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.92,1:14:27.98,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.72,1:14:29.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这边
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.88,1:15:12.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本来你弟弟 是要开除的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.24,1:15:15.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我们顾念他已经读到三年级了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.56,1:15:17.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我们记二个大过留校查看
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.92,1:15:20.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他还年轻嘛！对不对
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.08,1:15:22.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们给他一个自新的机会
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.08,1:15:25.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主要的是他级任老师 陶老师
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.88,1:15:27.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不愿意他留在这一班
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.64,1:15:29.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我们经过开会的结果
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.24,1:15:30.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就把他调一个班
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.28,1:15:34.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好！那就依陈教官的意思
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.16,1:15:36.54,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以后还麻烦教官多照顾他
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.80,1:16:53.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能够…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.00,1:16:57.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能够再活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.56,1:17:02.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没你的人生有如黑暗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.88,1:17:12.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请你快回来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.16,1:17:16.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你现在在那里
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.64,1:17:21.66,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心爱的那个人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.28,1:17:24.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能够…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.40,1:17:27.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能够再活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.80,1:17:32.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没你的人生有如黑暗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.32,1:17:34.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这块玉
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.32,1:17:36.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是你外婆从南洋带回来的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.68,1:17:40.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个戒子啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.52,1:17:42.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我十七岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.84,1:17:46.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外公从上海买给我做生日礼物的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.64,1:17:54.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看俊颖很瘦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.00,1:17:56.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要让他熬夜
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.32,1:17:59.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身体要紧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.60,1:18:02.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其它的都是假的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.88,1:18:07.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫁给你爸爸的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.44,1:18:10.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道他身体不好
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.44,1:18:13.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结婚二十年
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.88,1:18:16.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}足足服侍他二十年
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.76,1:18:28.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝！不要唱了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.16,1:18:30.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卖铜卖铁的 难听死了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.88,1:18:43.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我以前…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.56,1:18:48.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}教书的时候 有个男同事
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.12,1:18:51.42,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两个人很谈得来
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.72,1:18:55.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不敢跟我爸爸妈妈讲
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.84,1:18:59.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候真傻
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.32,1:19:01.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爸知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.92,1:19:07.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你爸爸很严肃
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.72,1:19:10.28,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一回到家就看书
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.40,1:19:12.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无声无息的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.24,1:19:16.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刚嫁过来的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.56,1:19:18.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还叫我读英文
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.04,1:19:20.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看不懂再问他
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.52,1:19:24.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结婚的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.08,1:19:27.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你阿公没事情做
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.16,1:19:30.72,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你爸爸家里又没钱
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.56,1:19:35.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我们旅行结婚
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.96,1:19:39.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连床都没买 很节省
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.32,1:19:48.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来回梅县 睡阿婆的床
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.28,1:19:53.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晚上的时候 被臭虫咬得要死
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.20,1:19:57.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二天我用热水拿来烫
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.08,1:20:00.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟你爸爸讲
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.76,1:20:03.32,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你爸爸很不高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.12,1:20:08.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说什么我们家哪有你家有钱
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.36,1:20:14.92,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一胎 生了你
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.04,1:20:16.63,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你阿婆不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.92,1:20:19.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二胎回家里生
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.52,1:20:22.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生了阿琴
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.28,1:20:26.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你阿婆很不高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.00,1:20:29.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说什么 只生女的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.20,1:20:32.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不帮我洗尿布
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.72,1:20:35.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐月子的第三天
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.68,1:20:39.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就自己到池塘边洗尿布
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.56,1:20:43.55,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}泪水滴滴答答
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.40,1:20:50.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候 听人讲
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.12,1:20:52.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去抱个男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.56,1:20:56.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是阿庆牯
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.04,1:21:02.27,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿庆牯和阿琴两个人一起喝奶
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.92,1:21:06.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后来奶水不够了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.92,1:21:10.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿琴先断奶 给阿庆牯吃
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.96,1:21:14.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿琴断奶的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.60,1:21:17.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还会喊我
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.00,1:21:21.51,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈妈吃奶奶
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.00,1:21:28.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我吓得躲在蚊帐后面 不敢出声
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.44,1:21:34.71,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一天
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.24,1:21:37.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆带阿琴去祠堂玩
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.88,1:21:39.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃到了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.84,1:21:43.75,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜神的东西 不干净
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.36,1:21:48.35,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到了晚上 又吐又泻
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.64,1:21:52.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想带她去梅县 又那么远
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.20,1:21:56.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在药铺拿药给她吃
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.12,1:22:00.03,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃了就止住了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.76,1:22:04.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}半夜 肚子硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.20,1:22:08.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二天
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.80,1:22:10.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就死了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.08,1:23:53.30,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.12,1:23:58.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.20,1:24:07.18,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.56,1:24:13.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去买一罐酱油
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.00,1:24:20.22,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.80,1:24:23.43,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看看我舌头后面长了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.56,1:24:30.86,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}里面好像有长小肉
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.00,1:28:16.67,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.32,1:28:22.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么还不去睡
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.24,1:28:23.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我起来上厕所
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.84,1:28:28.19,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.08,1:28:36.99,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我写信给你姊姊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.40,1:28:40.78,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天到医院检查
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.80,1:28:44.95,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}医生说要切片
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.72,1:28:48.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.56,1:28:50.78,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喉癌
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.16,1:29:32.87,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家里没人煮饭
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.60,1:29:35.83,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆没人看着就不见了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.56,1:29:38.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿忠在小港教书
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.56,1:29:40.11,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又没办法回来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.24,1:29:43.23,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我实在不放心
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.12,1:29:45.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿孝会做啦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.92,1:29:47.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煮饭、洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.04,1:29:50.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他不是连缝衣机都会用吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.44,1:29:51.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只要每天晚上
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.44,1:29:54.39,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把第二天便当的菜准备好就行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.56,1:29:57.31,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿婆就请对面的王妈妈照顾一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.84,1:30:01.91,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对啊！我星期三 星期六
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.04,1:30:03.59,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期天 没课
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.72,1:30:05.07,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都可以回来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.08,1:30:10.15,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且台北的医院设备比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.28,1:30:11.79,chs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}医生又多
